ZH: 我们都应该爱惜地球资源。
EN: We should all cherish the resources of the earth.

ZH: 爱惜时间，因为时间不等人。
EN: Cherish time, because time waits for no one.

ZH: 我们要爱惜公共设施，不要随意破坏。
EN: We should cherish public facilities and not vandalize them.

ZH: 爱惜生命，不要轻易冒险。
EN: Cherish life and do not take unnecessary risks.

ZH: 孩子们应该爱惜自己的玩具。
EN: Children should cherish their toys.

ZH: 爷爷奶奶给予我们的爱应该倍加珍惜。
EN: The love our grandparents give us should be cherished.

ZH: 我们要爱惜身体，多锻炼、合理饮食。
EN: We should cherish our bodies, exercise more and eat healthily.

ZH: 爱惜树木，保护环境。
EN: Cherish trees and protect the environment.

ZH: 每个社会成员都应该爱惜公德心。
EN: Every member of society should cherish public morality.

ZH: 珍惜友情，爱惜和朋友在一起的时光。
EN: Treasure friendship and cherish the time spent with friends.

ZH: 我们要爱惜劳动成果，不要浪费。
EN: We should cherish the fruits of our labor and not waste them.

ZH: 学会爱惜精力，提高工作效率。
EN: Learn to cherish energy and improve work efficiency.

ZH: 请爱惜公共设施，让大家都能共享资源。
EN: Please cherish public facilities so that everyone can share resources.

ZH: 爱惜水资源，避免浪费。
EN: Cherish water resources and avoid wastage.

ZH: 邻居间应该爱惜和睦相处。
EN: Neighbors should cherish getting along harmoniously.

ZH: 节约用水，爱惜环境。
EN: Conserve water and cherish the environment.

ZH: 保持干净整洁的生活环境是我们每个人的责任，要爱惜家园。
EN: Keeping a clean and tidy living environment is the responsibility of each of us, we must cherish our home.

ZH: 爱惜动物，不要虐待。
EN: Cherish animals and do not abuse them.

ZH: 爱惜青春年华，珍惜年轻时光。
EN: Cherish youth and treasure young time.
